Three products. Three intensities. From beginner to expert, level up your eye looks with The Climax Collection. Field Trainer for NARS UK & ROI, @renatomkp, shows you how in this three-part series for every skill level. 

LEVEL 1: SUBTLE SMOKE 
TO PREP: 
Radiant Creamy Concealer in Custard
Soft Velvet Loose Powder in Eden

TO LINE:
“Stamp, then perfect. This technique is perfect for beginners, as you don’t have to create a perfect line in one sweep.” —@renatomkp

HOW TO DO IT:
“Use the thin side of Climax Liquid Eyeliner and press it between the lashes. Keep doing this until you have your entire lash line covered with a thin layer. Then, use the point of the eyeliner to perfect any gaps.”

Climax Eyeshadow Palette in shades Private Show, Passion Play, and Public Eye
Climax Liquid Eyeliner
Climax Mascara
